headline: Children's Home Society of Idaho Receives $300,000 Grant From KeyBank to Support Mental Health for Treasure Valley Youth
summary: BOISE, ID / ACCESSWIRE / December 6, 2024 / KeyBank has awarded a $300,000 grant to Children's Home Society of Idaho (the Children's Home) to support expansion of the nonprofit's Care Farm Therapy Program for Treasure Valley children and adolescents ...
